Money Stuff =0A The big news today is that DeepSeek blew up the stock marke=
t: Chinese =0Aartificial intelligence startup DeepSeek=E2=80=99s latest AI =
model sparked a $ =0A=0A=0A <> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomberg.com/click=3Fs=
=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12430446&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525=
&p=3D01272025>=0A=0A=0A=0ADeepSeek=0A=0AThe big news today is that DeepSeek=
 blew up the stock market <>:=0A=0AChinese artificial intelligence startup =
DeepSeek=E2=80=99s latest AI model sparked a =0A$1 trillion rout in US and =
European technology stocks, as investors questioned =0Abloated valuations f=
or some of America=E2=80=99s biggest companies.=0A=0ADeepSeek=E2=80=99s lat=
est AI model rose to the top of the Apple=E2=80=99s appstore charts over =
=0Athe weekend, presenting a visible challenge to costlier models like Open=
AI and =0Araising questions over the hundreds of billions in planned spendi=
ng on the =0Atechnology by the likes of Microsoft Corp., Meta Platforms Inc=
